01:10:02,439 --> 01:10:05,807
I mean, the young woman
who plays the lead.

1409
01:10:05,809 --> 01:10:08,210
The couple who's in the house.

1410
01:10:08,212 --> 01:10:11,913
They're just that average
working class American.

1411
01:10:11,915 --> 01:10:14,482
And here were these
fearful things coming

1412
01:10:14,484 --> 01:10:17,719
