Teamwork.

1430
01:11:14,543 --> 01:11:16,544
Science.

1431
01:11:19,815 --> 01:11:21,816
Young love.

1432
01:11:24,987 --> 01:11:26,988
The patriarchal family.

1433
01:11:31,927 --> 01:11:33,928
The media.

1434
01:11:35,264 --> 01:11:37,265
The government.

1435
01:11:39,835 --> 01:11:42,337
And the police and military.

1436
01:11:45,741 --> 01:11:48,310
